document_data.name: Temple of Nephthys
document_data.mainbody: The '''Temple of Nephthys''' was a temple dedicated to the worship of [[Nephthys]], the [[god]] of commerce within the [[Mulhorandi pantheon]].{{Cite interactive atlas|490 Skuld}}
document_data.Location: The temple was located in the southwest section of the city of [[Skuld]] in the [[Skuld/Merchant District|Merchant District]] near the waterfront of the [[Alamber Sea]] and north of the [[River of Shadows]]. The temple sat just west of [[Bridge Street (Skuld)|Bridge Street]].
